        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【孩子“装病”？医生：“不，可能是心病”[开学季]】男娃突然全身无力，抽血时都反常不哭闹；女娃“癫痫”、满床翻滚，但俩人各项检查指标都正常。到底生了啥“...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【孩子“装病”？医生：“不，可能是心病”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[开学季]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】男娃突然全身无力，抽血时都反常不哭闹；女娃“癫痫”、满床翻滚，但俩人各项检查指标都正常。到底生了啥“怪病”？只好请专家来看。 医生“抽丝剥茧”，得出结论：其实他们得的是“心病”<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>在儿童医院急诊科，经常闹这样的“乌龙”，连医生都真假难辨。遇到这种情况，家长不要无情戳破。孩子未必是故意的，紧张、压力大等心理因素也会影响生理状况👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%97%AA%E9%97%AA%E7%9A%84%E5%84%BF%E7%A7%91%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#闪闪的儿科医生#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4909942763880551" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">深圳卫健委的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/orj480/a8bfee30gy1hepg7z9uqmj21hc0u0wlu.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/dBy9JRlbgx0862NESUog010412017xAw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686192070&amp;ssig=grPeCSF1%2BX&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/i67lbE9Igx0862NDklu001041200C6tm0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686192070&amp;ssig=3GXfwgfolM&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/BP2UhfVagx0862NDB1nG01041200p7E90E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1686192070&